{"tid":2175576,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國宣佈制裁中交建等24間參與南海建島中國企業","createTime":"2020-08-26T14:14:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T11:45:13.000Z","uid":122940,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8cb0742234da09bcec4f50df5a280d185328570f","tid":2175576,"uid":122940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T14:14:53.000Z","msg":"1800 子公司被美帝制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200826/7BPXGKYR4NBV5HZQTKTFSR6LGU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200826%2F7BPXGKYR4NBV5HZQTKTFSR6LGU%2F&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatgVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=43cee450\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200826%2F7BPXGKYR4NBV5HZQTKTFSR6LGU%2F&h=6f973692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200826/7BPXGKYR4NBV5HZQTKTFSR6LGU/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國再對中國出招。美國商務部26日宣佈，將24間中國企業，包括在港上市的中交建（1800）旗下5家公司，列入「實體清單」（Entity List）制裁，原因是它們協助中國在南海興建軍事用途的人工島及設施。<br />\n<br />\n美國工業安全局（BIS）指中國無視國際反對，自2013年起快速在南海興建具軍事用途的人工島，破壞美國在南海地區的合作夥伴的主權，決定將24間參與興建、涵蓋工程、通訊和導航的公司，列入商務部制裁名單。<br />\n<br />\n商務部部長羅斯（Wilbur Ross）表示，美國、中國的鄰國及國際社會均指摘中國在南海的主權要求，指「今日新增的實體清單在中國建設這些具挑釁性的人工島上，具有顯著作用，必須追究它們的責任。」<br />\n<br />\n商務部指，中國自2013年，在南海興建7個面積逾3,000畝的人工軍事建築，部份已部署防空和反艦導彈。又指，上述的人工島所在的位置，侵犯了菲律賓的主權。而荷蘭海牙的常設仲裁法院（PCA）已在2016年7月，裁定中國在上述區域所宣稱的權利無效。所以決定啟動制裁。<br />\n<br />\n受制裁的24間中國企業中，包括中國交通建設集團旗下5間公司、中船重工集團第722研究所、中國電子科技集團等分公司。"},{"pid":"a93eb2ced8550176ed633d79727d3a5fc6864b12","tid":2175576,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T14:17:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31e2697f2164324b1a09b8e8ebf3a7a71b9ec3a5","tid":2175576,"uid":287751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T14:19:45.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\">【行動 Post 請置頂】八三一週年，手足歸隊啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2175581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2175581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span>"},{"pid":"a060c3e706c1261c363b926dcb6261c23b06aea7","tid":2175576,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T15:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0d5789b7690d1edc8fec20eed745eefba68ab5","tid":2175576,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T15:12:30.000Z","msg":"新界北總區副指揮官曾正科交代及回應記者元朗721事件<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2175647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2175647</a>"},{"pid":"f464eee72659fc5d3860080547300bf91d8269a6","tid":2175576,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T15:13:14.000Z","msg":"中國又贏"},{"pid":"67bef76f15b03aaba78bf2de07be488a620c13b0","tid":2175576,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T20:55:30.000Z","msg":"Wow"},{"pid":"8487d44f8c2869fdc306a07137e772ce11b5c1ba","tid":2175576,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T21:07:12.000Z","msg":"等睇堅決反對"},{"pid":"76fe7a20e9726593acae280096930efd7d503ca0","tid":2175576,"uid":122940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8487d44f8c2869fdc306a07137e772ce11b5c1ba","tid":2175576,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T21:07:12.000Z","msg":"等睇堅決反對"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:03:34.000Z","msg":"無激烈回應"},{"pid":"124874d9d3af4a26328bb2763461f4f8885aa46b","tid":2175576,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:07:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.